---
alwaysApply: true
---
- Use FastAPI or Django REST Framework for API endpoints
- Always use Pydantic models for data validation
- All API endpoints must have type hints and docstrings
- Use async/await for database operations
- Follow PEP 8 strictly; max line length 88 (Black formatter)
- Use SQLAlchemy ORM, never raw SQL strings
- All exceptions must be handled with proper HTTP status codes
- Environment variables via python-dotenv, never hardcode secrets
- Write pytest tests for all endpoints; minimum 80% coverage
